{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-049-050-at-the-butcher-s",
    "title": "Lesson 49: At the butcher's",
    "audioFilename": "049&050－At the Butcher's.mp3",
    "duration": 82.312,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.34,
      "end": 2.02,
      "text": "Lesson 49.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第49课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.94,
      "end": 5.6,
      "text": "At the Butcher's.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "在肉店。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.6,
      "end": 9.82,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 11.58,
      "end": 12.8,
      "text": "What does Mr. Bird",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "伯德先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 13.2,
      "end": 13.74,
      "text": "like?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "喜欢什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 15.72,
      "end": 18.82,
      "text": "Do you want any meat today, Mrs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "今天要买肉吗，伯德"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 19.2,
      "end": 19.22,
      "text": "Bird?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "太太？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 20.56,
      "end": 21.56,
      "text": "Yes, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "要的，谢谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 23.22,
      "end": 26.06,
      "text": "Do you want beef or lamb?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您要牛肉还是羊肉？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 27.12,
      "end": 28.04,
      "text": "Beef, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请给我牛肉。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 29.2,
      "end": 31.9,
      "text": "This lamb's very good.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这羊肉很好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 33.6,
      "end": 37.44,
      "text": "I like lamb, but my husband doesn't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我喜欢羊肉，但我丈夫不喜欢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 38.6,
      "end": 40.42,
      "text": "What about some steak?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "来点牛排怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 41.56,
      "end": 43.66,
      "text": "This is a nice piece.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这块很好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 44.9,
      "end": 47.2,
      "text": "Give me that piece, please.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请把那块给我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 48.38,
      "end": 51.08,
      "text": "And a pound of mince, too.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "再来一磅肉馅。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 52.9,
      "end": 55.8,
      "text": "Do you want a chicken, Mrs. Bird?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "伯德太太，您要只鸡吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 57.28,
      "end": 59,
      "text": "They're very nice.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这些鸡都很好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 59.86,
      "end": 61.08,
      "text": "No, thank you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不了，谢谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 62.26,
      "end": 66.96,
      "text": "My husband likes steak, but he doesn't like chicken.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我丈夫喜欢牛排，但他不喜欢鸡肉。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 68.68,
      "end": 71.38,
      "text": "To tell you the truth, Mrs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "说实话，伯德太太，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 72.74,
      "end": 75.5,
      "text": "I don't like chicken either.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我也不喜欢鸡肉。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
